A standardized Wiki markup language. 

Standardization of version 1.0 is documented here [[http://www.wikicreole.org/|http://www.wikicreole.org/]]

NicFerrier is writing EmacsLisp handling of WikiCreole. His current package is in [[http://marmalade-repo.org/packages/creole/0.7.2|marmalade]].

More information about Creole related to OddMuse, the software that runs EmacsWiki, see [[Oddmuse:Creole Markup Extension]]

